# Project Overview

This is an Astro-based web application using modern web technologies. The project uses:
- [astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs) as the main Astro configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) for dependencies and scripts
- TypeScript with [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) configuration
- Panda CSS for styling with [panda.config.ts](mdc:panda.config.ts)
- ESLint for code quality with [eslint.config.js](mdc:eslint.config.js)

## Project Structure
- `src/` - Main source code directory
- `public/` - Static assets
- `styled-system/` - Generated Panda CSS styles
- `.astro/` - Astro build artifacts
- `dist/` - Production build output
